    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pumpkin Hack</strong> is a <strong>third-person multiplayer action game</strong> with a mix of <strong>stealth</strong> and <strong>combat mechanics</strong>. Players start as regular pumpkins, blending into the environment to avoid detection. You can <strong>crawl, walk, and sprint</strong> to outmaneuver enemies — but when the time is right, transform into a monstrous form with powerful scythe attacks. Collect seeds to refill stamina, dodge enemy strikes, and bait opponents into traps. Strategic hiding and timing are key to survival!</p>",
